Was Petya a Cover-Up for Prior Attacks?

Was Petya a Cover-Up for Prior Attacks?


          Booz Allen Cyber4Sight analyzed attacks predating the Petya outbreak but still using the same obscure Ukrainian M.E.Doc tax software to ensnare victims and found that the Petya outbreak may have actually been destroy forensic information and cover up for prior attacks.
