    The right people, solving problems with purpose and passion 



Booz Allen created the concept of management consulting more than a century ago. Since then, we've woven that heritage into a range of highly skilled technological capabilities that have had an enduring impact for our clients, our people, and the communities where we live and work.
Our people bring a mix of expertise to solve problems with a different, more effective mindset, devising powerful solutions for our clients’ toughest challenges. We’ve lasted more than 100 years because we’ve stood firm on a foundation of the highest character, and unyielding commitment to the best client service.
We’ve adapted with the needs of the times, building value and opportunity by investing in technology sectors such as data science and analytics, digital solutions, engineering, and cybersecurity. And we're supporting those skills with investments in our culture of innovation, empowering our 22,600 dedicated employees as creative thinkers.
We all share a defining characteristic—a driving passion to solve our clients’ problems and deliver lasting value. 





