    Our Core Areas 



Our culture of innovation empowers employees as creative thinkers, bringing unparalleled value for our clients and to any problem we tackle.








Consulting
 Government and commercial organizations face increasing pressure to improve services, mitigate risk, and aggressively pursue new strategic initiatives. Our management consulting services empower clients to transform and thrive. 
Read More






Analytics
 Our team of more than 600 data scientists—one of the largest in the market—thinks bigger, pushes further, and asks the questions others don’t. And we’ve embraced the complexities of a world that's more connected and generating more data.  
Read More






Digital Solutions
 Our people are putting their passion to work in revolutionary ways, solving today’s most complex problems with brilliant ideas and innovative expertise and taking technologies and software products to another level.  
Read More






Engineering
 Our 3,000 engineers and applied scientists don’t just come up with the ideas to change the way our world works—we help build them, fundamentally changing how we approach threats to civilians, soldiers, and citizens. 
Read More






Cyber
 With decades of mission intelligence combined with the most advanced tools available, we script solutions that disrupt without disturbing, protecting clients against the attacks of today and preparing them for the threats of tomorrow. 
Read More























