A Roadmap to High Reliability in Military Health

A Roadmap to High Reliability in Military Health


          Booz Allen’s consultants are working with the U.S. Military Health Services to overcome these challenges and more. By devising and implementing a plan that accounts for every step, every layer, and every contingency, they’re helping one of the world’s largest and most bureaucratically complex healthcare organizations go from frequently falling below industry benchmarks to exceeding them.
