    Our Capabilities 









Management Consulting
More than just analyzing problems and developing plans for better performance, our management consultants respond to the demands of today’s data-driven digital economy with knowledge management strategies, process improvement tools, and organizational design insights. And our change management experts support organizational change and apply multiple disciplines to manage the natural cycle and effects of change. The result is desired end-state sustainable across changes in personnel and leadership.







Human Capital and Learning
We provide clients a strategic roadmap and proven tactics to maximize human capital. By engaging audiences in meaningful learning, we boost recruiting, onboarding, development and retention. 







Strategic Communications
Communication drives everything we do as a society. We’re evolving our strategic work in a digital, disruptive environment.







Acquisition, Program Management, and Logistics
We help program and contract managers succeed within the current acquisition system—one marked by shrinking budgets and heightened expectations and scrutiny—by helping streamline the existing process with multidimensional thinking, skills, and tools.









Wargaming
For more than 50 years, we’ve designed these exercises to give clients a conceptual framework to better understand the future or the unknown, often in dynamic and adversarial settings. We’ll help you solve your toughest challenges—and make you better.  






