Booz Allen Hamilton Inc. (/ˈbuːz ˈælən ˈhæməltən/,[3] informally: Booz Allen[4]) is an American management consulting firm, sometimes referred to as a government-services company,[5] headquartered in McLean, Virginia,[6] in Greater Washington, D.C., with 80 other offices around the globe.



